      <title>2019 年以来，中国股息股表现远超成长股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-dividend-stocks-outperform-growth-peers-by-most-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于低迷的经济前景尚未给投资者转向成长型股票提供足够的动力，高股息收益率的中国股票继续受到投资者的青睐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-dividend-stocks-outperform-growth-peers-by-most-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
